      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'll try to clean it out first before calling anyone. does the black stuff usually mean the pipes are corroding or is it just old sediment from the water? i'm just trying to figure out if this is a simple washer fix or if i'm looking at a bigger problem with the whole valve assembly.",
